dct_title_s: Tourist map, the Holy Land, Palestine / published and designed by GSE, Good Shepherd Engineering & Computing, PalMap, Palestine Mapping Center. (Map)
dct_description_sm: Shows Palestine evacuated lands 2005, Oslo ABC zoning areas, and 7 classes of separation walls (including Green Line = armistice line 1949). Includes two insets: southern area continuation map (scale 1:750,000) -- Regional map. Also shows Golan Heights; parts of Lebanon, Syria, Jordan, and Egypt. Verso: Index to place names, international crossing points are listed and located.
dct_publisher_sm: Bethlehem, West Bank, Palestine : Palmap, Palestine Mapping Center, 2008.
